column1: I couldn't seem to experience any positive feeling at all
column2: I found it difficult to work up the initiative to do things
column3: I felt that I had nothing to look forward to
column5: I was unable to become enthusiastic about anything
column6: I felt I wasn't worth much as a person
column7: I felt that life was meaningless
column8: I was aware of dryness of my mouth
column9:
I experienced breathing difficulty (eg, excessively rapid breathing,

column10: I experienced trembling (eg, in the hands)
column11:
I was worried about situations in which I might panic and make

column12: I felt I was close to panic
column13:
I was aware of the action of my heart in the absence of physical
exertion (eg, sense of heart rate increase, heart missing a beat)

column15: I found it hard to wind down

column19: I found it difficult to relax
column20:

column21: I felt that I was rather touchy
